  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Human Development Initiative Through Empowerment And Settlement Improvement In The Plantation Settlements In Sri Lanka</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Goal: 

Empowered
and resilient plantation communities with satisfactory living conditions, safer
settlements, better access to basic services and improved livelihood skills.Towards this, there are 3 main
objectives: &#xB7;
To empower communities and increase employability of youth&#xB7;
To improve resilience and access to infrastructure facilities in
plantation settlements&#xB7;To facilitate mainstreaming of the plantation settlements into the
administrative procedures</narrative>
  </description>
